Feedback Report: Phase 5, Step 1 Update

Issue: Permission denied when connecting to docker.sock despite running usermod.
Cause: On Bazzite (Fedora Atomic), the system docker group is not present in the writable /etc/group file by default, causing usermod to fail silently or effectively do nothing.

Proposed Update for Phase 5, Step 1:
Insert this command before usermod to sync the system group to the local configuration:

